OL,5, Izzy, who is 18 and works at           
OL,6, McDonald's, says she is still          
OL,7, witnessing "disgusting behaviour",     
OL,8, months after the BBC revealed sexual   
OL,9, abuse claims at the fast food chain.   
OL,11,FShe is one of more than 160 people who 
OL,12,Fhave approached the BBC with new       
OL,13,Fallegations after our investigation.   
OL,15,FThey include claims of sexual assault, 
OL,16,Fharassment, racism and bullying.       
OL,18,FMcDonald's said it was "determined" to 
OL,19,Froot out behaviour that falls below the
OL,20,Fhigh standards it expects of staff.    
